msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	104	6260	6156"
msgid "I could only entrust the task\\r\n"
"to someone I trusted unconditionally."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	214	6481	6267"
msgid "Only natural then for me to give the\\r\n"
"responsibility to Mayumi, my own flesh and blood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	238	6872	6634"
msgid "Though, had I known what kind of man\\r\n"
"Kazuma Kiryu was from the get-go..."
